column2: "Congratulations! We've been able to assemble half of the data you've collected."
"It seems that the area was embodied by Ether, from the residual energy after Omega's disappearance. It's why the resemblance is uncanny."
"Now the impact on Oracle is limited, however the energy signatures of Ephimera are worrisome. So I would like to do more research on the matter a bit more."
"Anyways <%me>, thank you for your continued assistance!"
